00:44:09.310 --> 00:44:10.960
into the platform.

00:44:10.960 --> 00:44:13.780
So you can use
that specific example or I mean, if there's

00:44:13.780 --> 00:44:17.240
other examples that you've sort of encountered
where good intentions can lead us astray.

00:44:17.240 --> 00:44:20.790
I mean, it's something that we kind of keep
in the back of our minds, I think, at Google

00:44:20.790 --> 00:44:22.660
because we are building these
platforms--[fades out]

00:44:22.660 --> 00:44:23.660
&gt;&gt;Steve Johnson: Yeah.

